n de frases alterada (24, 26);\\Nerrores fonológicos (32) → afectación temporal posterior y parietal\\Ninferior (Figura 3b-c) (42, 53, 64).","guid":"OXuE5fbUj0Do44Uc6m06XA","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"5","text":"• Neuropatología → Enfermedad de\\NAlzheimer (EA) (29) (Figura 5a, 6).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"5","text":"• Criterios Dx (24):","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"5","text":"• Necesarios:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"5","text":"• Dificultad para\\Nencontrar palabras","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"5","text":"• Repetición\\Nalterada de frases.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"5","text":"• Al menos 3:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"5","text":"• Errores fonológicos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"5","text":"• Comprensión de palabras\\Nsimples y objetos preservada.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"5","text":"• Motricidad del\\Nhabla intacta.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"5","text":"• Ausencia de\\Nagramatismo.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"44","parent":"0","text":"Etiología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"• Neurodegeneración (1, 131, 132) → lóbulos\\Nfrontal y temporal del hemisferio dominante\\N(izquierdo en la mayoría) (16, 17).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"44","text":"• APP-G → FTLD\\N(proteína tau) (29).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"44","text":"• APP-S → FTLD\\N(proteína TDP-43-C) (29).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"44","text":"• APP-L → EA\\N(amiloide y tau) (29).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"• 3-4/100,000 (18); incidencia → 1.\\N14/100,000 personas-años (19).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"51","parent":"0","text":"Fisiopatología\\N(29, 133-135)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"• APP-G → Atrofia → lóbulo\\Nfrontal inferior dominante (área\\Nde Broca) e ínsula (53).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"51","text":"• APP-S → Atrofia → lóbulos\\Ntemporales anteriores, polos\\Ntemporales → predominio izquierdo\\N(66).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"51","text":"• APP-L → Atrofia → circunvoluciones\\Ntemporal superior y media posterior,\\Nlóbulo parietal inferior (42).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"55","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"• Clínico → Anamnesis → inicio insidioso, progresión\\Ngradual (15, 149, 150); evaluación del lenguaje →\\NNorthwestern Anagram Test (44, 45), Montreal Cognitive\\NAssessment (Precaución) (35).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"55","text":"• Imagen → RMN cerebral (Figura 1,\\N3) (26, 31), FDG-PET (26) → atrofia\\Nfocal según variante.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"55","text":"• RMN:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"55","text":"• APP-G ↓ sensibilidad (29%), ↑\\Nespecificidad (91%) → atrofia\\Nfrontal posterior (36-38).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"55","text":"• APP-S ↑ sensibilidad (98%), ↑\\Nespecificidad (93%) → atrofia\\Ntemporal anterior (39-41).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"55","text":"• APP-L ↓ sensibilidad (57%), ↑\\Nespecificidad (95%) → atrofia temporal\\Nposterior y parietal inferior (42).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"55","text":"• FDG-PET:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"55","text":"• APP-G sensibilidad (67%),\\Nespecificidad (92%) →\\Nhipometabolismo frontal posterior.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"55","text":"• APP-S sensibilidad (casi 100%),\\Nespecificidad (casi 100%) →\\Nhipometabolismo temporal anterior.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"55","text":"• APP-L sensibilidad (92%), especificidad\\N(94%) → hipometabolismo temporal\\Nposterior y parietal inferior.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"66","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento","guid":"","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"• Terapia del habla y lenguaje (153);\\NtDCS experimental (156-158).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"68","parent":"0","text":"Pronóstico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"• Supervivencia media → 7.1 - 12\\Naños según variante (47).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"70","parent":"0","text":"Dx Diferencial","guid":"","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"• Demencia, afasia isquémica, tumor\\Ncerebral, Alzheimer, FTD (3).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"0","text":"Complicaciones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"• Pérdida del habla/comprensión, depresión\\N(155), parkinsonismo (raro) (47).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"74","parent":"0","text":"Consultas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"75","parent":"74","text":"• Neurología,\\NFonoaudiología,\\NPsicología.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"76","parent":"0","text":"Factores de\\Nsusceptibilidad","guid":"","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"• Historia familiar o personal de problemas\\Nde aprendizaje (dislexia) (138, 139),\\Nautoinmunidad (140, 141).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"78","parent":"0","text":"Genética","guid":"","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"• Mutaciones en GRN, MAPT,\\NC9orf72, PSEN1 (raro) (142-145).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"80","parent":"0","text":"Biomarcadores\\N(Figura 7)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"• Imagen de amiloide-β por PET,\\Ncuantificación de tau y amiloide-β en LCR →\\Nprobabilidad de patología de AD (29).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"82","parent":"0","text":"Clasificación simplificada\\N(Figura 2) (26, 31)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"• PPA-G → Agramatismo, ↓\\Nfluidez, habla trabajosa.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"82","text":"• PPA-S → Anomia, ↓\\Ncomprensión palabras,\\Npreserva gramática y\\Nrepetición.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"82","text":"• PPA-L → ↓ fluidez por dificultad para\\Nencontrar palabras, preserva gramática y\\Ncomprensión de palabras simples.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"82","text":"• PPA-M → Combinación de\\Ngramática y comprensión alteradas.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"87","parent":"0","text":"Área de Wernicke","guid":"","children":[{"id":"88","parent":"87","text":"• Cuestionada su localización clásica (69,\\N96-98). Se propone red distribuida con mayor\\Npeso en ATL (60, 75, 80, 117).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"89","parent":"0","text":"Red del lenguaje","guid":"","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"• Componentes dorsales (IFG - Broca) → fonología,\\Nfluidez, gramática (1-5). Componentes ventrales (lóbulo\\Ntemporal) → lexicosemántico (1-5).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"0","text":"ATL","guid":"","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"• Rol crítico en la precisión de la denominación y\\Ncomprensión de palabras (66, 67, 73-77). Asimetría →\\Nizquierdo especializado en verbal (66, 83).","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":92,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Neurología","filename":"Afasia primaria progresiva (APP)-2025","id":"map_1384","resolved_references":[]}